equest has completed. A completion timestamp is recorded."},{"label":"Rejected","value":"An approver rejected the request. Terminal — does not advance. Requires a reason."},{"label":"Escalated","value":"The request was escalated, typically automatically after a step's escalation window elapsed."},{"label":"Cancelled","value":"The request was cancelled. Terminal."},{"label":"AutoApproved","value":"The amount fell below a step's auto-approve threshold and the step was approved automatically."}]},{"heading":"Decision Types (History)","items":[{"label":"Approve","value":"Approver accepts; the request moves to the next step or completes."},{"label":"Reject","value":"Approver rejects; comments are required and the request is terminal."},{"label":"Delegate","value":"Approver hands the decision to another user; the request stays at the same step under the delegate."},{"label":"Escalate","value":"The request is escalated — usually automatic when a step exceeds its escalation hours."}]},{"heading":"Workflows Tab (Admin / Manager only)","items":[{"label":"New Workflow button","value":"Opens the workflow create dialog. Green 'create' button in the workflows toolbar."},{"label":"Workflows table","value":"Lists all defined workflows. Columns: workflow name, entity type, Active/Inactive status chip, steps count, and created date. Rows are clickable to edit. tableId: approval-workflows"},{"label":"Active / Inactive chip","value":"Green 'Active' chip when the workflow is enabled, gray 'Inactive' chip when disabled."},{"label":"Edit (pencil icon)","value":"Opens the workflow editor dialog pre-filled with the workflow's settings and steps."}]},{"heading":"Workflow Editor — Header Fields","items":[{"label":"Workflow Name (required)","value":"Text input. The display name, e.g., 'PO Approval > $500'. Required to save."},{"label":"Entity Type (required)","value":"Select. Which entity this workflow approves: Purchase Order, Expense, Quote, Time Entry, or Sales Order. Required to save."},{"label":"Description","value":"Textarea, optional. Explains the workflow's purpose."},{"label":"Amount Threshold","value":"Number input, optional. The workflow only activates when the request amount is above this value."}]},{"heading":"Workflow Editor — Step Fields (Repeatable)","items":[{"label":"Step Number","value":"Display-only. Auto-numbered 1, 2, 3 in the order steps appear. Steps run sequentially."},{"label":"Step Name (required)","value":"Text input. The step's label, e.g., 'Manager Approval'."},{"label":"Approver Type","value":"Select. Who approves this step: Specific User, Role, or Manager (the requester's direct manager)."},{"label":"Role (conditional)","value":"Select, shown only when Approver Type is Role. Options: Admin, Manager, Office Manager, PM."},{"label":"Auto-Approve Below","value":"Number input, optional. If the request amount is under this value, the step auto-approves (status AutoApproved)."},{"label":"Escalate After (Hours)","value":"Number input, optional. If the step sits pending longer than this many hours, it auto-escalates."},{"label":"Add Step / Remove Step","value":"Add Step appends a new step to the chain. The trash icon removes a step (only shown when more than one step exists)."}]},{"heading":"Validation Rules","items":[{"label":"Workflow Name","value":"Required to save the workflow."},{"label":"Entity Type","value":"Required to save the workflow."},{"label":"Step Name","value":"Required on each step."},{"label":"At least one step","value":"The Save/Create button is disabled until the workflow has at least one step (and the form is valid)."},{"label":"Reject reason","value":"Required before a rejection can be confirmed in the inbox reject dialog."}]},{"heading":"Entity Types Approved","items":[{"label":"Purchase Order","value":"Purchase order authorization — the most common approval use case."},{"label":"Expense","value":"Expense report / reimbursement authorization."},{"label":"Quote","value":"Sales quote sign-off before it goes to